\sin(n\pi x + \pi x) = \sin(n\pi x)\cos (n\pi) + \sin(n\pi)\cos(n\pi x)
\sin(n\pi x + \pi x) = \sin(n\pi x)\cos (\pi x) + \sin(\pi x)\cos(n\pi x)
